---
---

<section class="action-blocks section-padding" id="ways-to-fight">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label animate-in" style="text-align:center;display:block;" data-i18n="volunteer.action_label">Ways to Fight</span>
    <h2 class="section-title animate-in" style="text-align:center;" data-i18n="volunteer.action_headline">Every Role Matters</h2>

    <div class="action-grid">
      <!-- Deep Canvassing -->
      <div class="action-card animate-in">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <span class="action-icon">🚪</span>
          <h3 class="action-title" data-i18n="volunteer.canvass_title">Deep Canvassing</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="action-desc" data-i18n="volunteer.canvass_desc">
          Knock on doors in Pilsen, Little Village, and the inner-ring suburbs to have meaningful, one-on-one conversations about housing, economic justice, and the fight against the machine. This is how movements are built: at the doorstep.
        </p>
        <span class="action-tag" data-i18n="volunteer.canvass_tag">In-Person • Weekends</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Precinct Captains -->
      <div class="action-card animate-in">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <span class="action-icon">📋</span>
          <h3 class="action-title" data-i18n="volunteer.precinct_title">Precinct Captains</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="action-desc" data-i18n="volunteer.precinct_desc">
          Lead the ground game in your neighborhood. Precinct captains coordinate local volunteers, organize signature drives, and serve as the backbone of the campaign at the block level. Not selected? Support your captain however you can.
        </p>
        <span class="action-tag" data-i18n="volunteer.precinct_tag">Leadership • Community</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Ticket-Splitting Education -->
      <div class="action-card animate-in">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <span class="action-icon">🗳️</span>
          <h3 class="action-title" data-i18n="volunteer.ticket_title">Ticket-Splitting Education</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="action-desc" data-i18n="volunteer.ticket_desc">
          As an independent, Byron will not benefit from the straight-ticket Democratic vote. We need educators to teach voters how to split their ticket in November to defy the machine and cast a vote for a real representative.
        </p>
        <span class="action-tag" data-i18n="volunteer.ticket_tag">Critical • Voter Education</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Digital Organizing -->
      <div class="action-card animate-in">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <span class="action-icon">📱</span>
          <h3 class="action-title" data-i18n="volunteer.digital_title">Digital Organizing & Phonebanking</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="action-desc" data-i18n="volunteer.digital_desc">
          Reach voters where they are through rapid-response text campaigns, phone calls, and social media. This work can be done from anywhere, anytime, and is critical for expanding the movement beyond what door-knocking alone can achieve.
        </p>
        <span class="action-tag" data-i18n="volunteer.digital_tag">Remote • Flexible Hours</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Social Media & Creative -->
      <div class="action-card animate-in">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <span class="action-icon">🎨</span>
          <h3 class="action-title" data-i18n="volunteer.creative_title">Social Media & Creative</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="action-desc" data-i18n="volunteer.creative_desc">
          Design flyers, create campaign videos, and push content across social media. From graphic design to videography and video editing, your creative skills can amplify Byron's message to thousands of voters.
        </p>
        <span class="action-tag" data-i18n="volunteer.creative_tag">Remote • Graphic Design • Video</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Campus & Youth Organizing -->
      <div class="action-card animate-in">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <span class="action-icon">🎓</span>
          <h3 class="action-title" data-i18n="volunteer.campus_title">Campus & Youth Organizing</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="action-desc" data-i18n="volunteer.campus_desc">
          High school ambassadors and college campus captains help mobilize the next generation. Organize voter registration drives, host campus events, and build a youth coalition that fights for affordable education and a livable future.
        </p>
        <span class="action-tag" data-i18n="volunteer.campus_tag">Students • Young Voters</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .action-blocks {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .action-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .action-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--blue);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    transition: transform var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default), box-shadow var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default);
  }

  .action-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .action-card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .action-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .action-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .action-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .action-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--orange);
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(5, 173, 237, 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .action-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
